    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">A word ladder is a sequence of words of the same length where each word in the sequence changes exactly one letter in the previous word. Here's an example of a word ladder connecting &quot;mate&quot; and &quot;vial&quot;:<br><pre style=\"font-family: monospace\"><br>mate<br>mite<br>mile<br>mill<br>dill<br>dial<br>vial<br></pre><br>Given the terms of an attempted word ladder, determine whether it is valid. That is, all the words should be the <const>same length</const>, and each step should result from changing exactly one letter. Also, there should be <const>no duplicates</const> among the words, and there should be <const>at least 2 words</const>.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> An integer <var>N</var>, denoting the number of terms in the word ladder.<br><strong>Next N lines:</strong> Strings <var>S</var>, each containing only lowercase values.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> Either &quot;true&quot; or &quot;false&quot;, depending on the validity of the word ladder.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le; <var>N</var> &le; 60<br>1 &le; <var>Length of S</var> &le; 60</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">7\nmate\nmite\nmile\nmill\ndill\ndial\nvial</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">true</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
